#. type: Title ##
#, no-wrap
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Pregled"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"NV Speech Player is a free and open-source prototype speech synthesizer that "
"can be used by NVDA. It generates speech using Klatt synthesis, making it "
"somewhat similar to speech synthesizers such as Dectalk and Eloquence."
msgstr ""
"NV Speech Player je eksperimentalna govorna jedinica otvorenog koda i može "
"se koristiti u NVDA čitaču. NV Speech Player generira govor koristeći Klatt "
"sintezu te je sličan govornim jedinicama kao što su Dectalk i Eloquence."

